1
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,240
The audacity

2
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:41,320
Men at their birth are naturally good.

3
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:46,000
Their natures are similar, but their habits differ.

4
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:50,160
If not taught, their nature will change.

5
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,200
Brother Yao Yuan

6
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,080
Sworn brother

7
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:53,520
Mm

8
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:56,080
Come on, go have some candy.

9
00:02:59,240 --> 00:02:59,600
Go on, go on.

10
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,360
Time for candy!

11
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,880
Seeing such a worried look on your face, Sworn Brother,

12
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:06,960
is there still no progress on the case?

13
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:16,960
Do not worry, Sworn Brother.

14
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:18,480
With your skills, Sworn Brother,

15
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,080
no matter how cunning the criminal is,

16
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,720
he cannot escape your grasp.

17
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:23,640
The sky has cleared.

18
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:26,560
All brothels in Chang'an City are on guard.

19
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:27,720
It won't be easy for him to strike.

20
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,560
That is a good thing.

21
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,360
His plan is not yet complete.

22
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:33,960
I worry that next,

23
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:35,640
he will stop choosing specific targets

24
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:36,800
and kill indiscriminately.

25
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:45,640
Xi Rou, you must be careful too.

26
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,120
Watch out for this man.

27
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,400
Do not go out after dark.

28
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,400
Nightfall is only ten hours away.

29
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,520
Xi Rou, I will take my leave now.

30
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,080
Rest assured, Sworn Brother.

31
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:10,320
You must also be careful, Sworn Brother.

32
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:11,760
Mm

33
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:23,960
My Lord

34
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:25,840
We went to every Puppet Maker's shop in Chang'an.

35
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:27,240
We bought from them all. Everything is here.

36
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:28,400
You didn't arouse suspicion, did you?

37
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,000
No.

38
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:30,000
Good.

39
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:33,240
My Lord

40
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:34,240
Mm

41
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:38,520
Everyone, the culprit's mask is of excellent craftsmanship.

42
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,240
The file marks are as fine as hair.

43
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,200
Tung oil was mixed into the lacquer,

44
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:43,440
giving it an excellent sheen.

45
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:45,280
The red lacquer contains a large amount of cinnabar,

46
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:46,440
making it as red as blood.

47
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,280
There are six layers of lacquer coating.

48
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:50,640
Compare them one by one based on these characteristics.

49
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:52,640
Get me results within an hour.

50
00:04:53,320 --> 00:04:53,600
Yes, sir.

51
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,880
Candied hawthorns!

52
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:15,920
Mom, I want candied hawthorns.

53
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,400
One skewer of candied hawthorns. Coming right up.

54
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,560
You're only allowed to have one.

55
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:21,720
Careful not to rot your teeth.

56
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:22,280
Okay.

57
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:23,920
Let's go.

58
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:24,760
Take care.

59
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:29,640
It's so yummy.

60
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,240
A portrait of mother and son.

61
00:05:42,320 --> 00:05:43,680
He paints on the victims' bodies,

62
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:46,400
depicting the love he yearns for.

63
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:49,120
His targets are all prostitutes.

64
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:52,800
Could it be that his mother was a prostitute?

65
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,360
His origins made him feel inferior,

66
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,080
so he disfigured his own face.

67
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:57,480
Hatred born of malice,

68
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:00,240
driving him to kill every prostitute in the world.

69
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:05,400
If so, it all makes sense.

70
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,320
Why would it be him?

71
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:16,400
Is his kindness all just a disguise?

72
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:17,960
Look at mine.

73
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:36,880
Xi Rou

74
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,080
Liu Tong

75
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:40,520
Brother

76
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:43,560
Where are you going?

77
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,240
The children are hungry.

78
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:47,920
I'm going to buy some food.

79
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:50,960
No need. I brought snacks and candied fruit.

80
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:54,600
Children,

81
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:58,280
look what delicious treats Brother brought you.

82
00:06:58,920 --> 00:06:59,440
Yummy treats!

83
00:07:00,280 --> 00:07:01,080
Candied fruit!

84
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:02,160
Come here.

85
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,200
Candied fruit.

86
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,280
There's enough for everyone.

87
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:04,800
I want some!

88
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,120
Here.

89
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,120
Xi Rou,

90
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:10,320
how is the investigation of your sworn brother's case going?

91
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:12,800
No progress.

92
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:14,680
Brother,

93
00:07:15,320 --> 00:07:17,160
what happened to your leg?

94
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:18,640
Oh.

95
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,120
I fell. It's nothing.

96
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:24,200
Then I... I'll go get you some medicine.

97
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:34,480
Xi Rou.

98
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,640
I heard Lord Yao

99
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:42,760
has already drawn a portrait of the culprit.

100
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:43,640
Really?

101
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:46,440
It's just rumors from the streets.

102
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,240
My sworn brother isn't that amazing.

103
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:56,280
Brother,

104
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,520
it's been gloomy for days,

105
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,040
but the sky has finally cleared.

106
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:04,040
Let's go out and get some sun.

107
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:09,640
Let me apply some medicine for you.

108
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:12,440
All right.

109
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:37,440
Master,

110
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,800
this mask...

111
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,480
is it from your shop?

112
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:48,920
This item is indeed from my humble shop.

113
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,680
You gentlemen are wearing official uniforms.

114
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:53,400
Why?

115
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:56,280
Is there a problem with this item?

116
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:57,960
There is a big problem.

117
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:00,480
Regarding the recent murder in Chang'an City,

118
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,640
this is a key piece of evidence.

119
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:10,040
It seems you suspect this old man.

120
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,040
Master, you misunderstand.

121
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:21,920
The murderer has been captured by the Dali Temple.

122
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,400
He felt this mask was very valuable,

123
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,200
so he asked us to return it to you.

124
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:41,560
You caught the wrong person.

125
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:45,920
I am the real murderer.
